						<div class="postbody">Organize with whatever works best.  I mainly make directories for data that has many parts to it.
<br />
<br />I have directories for Level and tileset data, enemy data, music, and CHR data.  Everything else seems general enough to stick in the root directory.
<br />
<br />But there's not really any standard.</div>

